                <h1>Uber Background Check Disqualifiers Explained</h1>
                <p>Uber background checks are essential to ensure safety and reliability. Disqualifiers include felony convictions, DUI or drug-related offenses within the past seven years, driving record issues like reckless driving, and failure to report accidents. Any serious criminal history can result in disqualification, impacting your opportunity to drive.</p>
